                     <interp inst="t18220417-92-person891" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was indebted to Mr. Smith 4 l.; the prisoner called for it several times, and at last I paid him four sovereigns, and produce the receipt he wrote me for it.</p>
               <p>(read).</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I always wished to settle by instalments.</p>
